data.description: Welcome to your dream ranch in Pueblo, CO! This stunning 5-acre property offers everything you need for a perfect country lifestyle. With an irrigation well and a 3-acre pasture, this ranch is ideal for equestrian enthusiasts or anyone seeking a spacious and picturesque retreat.  The ranch features a well-maintained barn, complete with a tack room that includes a convenient shower. Additionally, a detached shop and sheds provide ample space for storage and hobbies. The pens and corrals are thoughtfully designed to accommodate various livestock needs.  The centerpiece of the property is a charming brick 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom house, spanning over 3000 square feet. Step inside and be greeted by gleaming hardwood floors and new carpet, exuding warmth and comfort. The expansive kitchen is a chef's delight, offering plenty of room for culinary creations and memorable gatherings.  Enjoy the serene beauty of the surrounding landscape from the comfort of your own backyard. Whether you desire a peaceful evening by the fire or a lively barbecue with friends, this ranch provides the perfect setting.  To ensure convenience and efficiency, automatic waterers are placed in the corals, ensuring a constant supply of water for your animals.  Don't miss the opportunity to own this exceptional ranch, offering the perfect balance of rural tranquility and modern comforts. Embrace the charm of country living while being just a short drive away from the vibrant city of Pueblo.
